title: Stakker Eurotechno (1989) HQ VHS RIP (DEINTERLACED)

WARNING: THIS RARE VIDEO CONTAINS FLASHING STROBE LIGHT IMAGES

Eurotechno is an early project released by Brian Dougans in 1989 under the name Stakker. It was originally a soundtrack to a visual work released on Virgin Vision by Colin Scott, Mark McLean and Marek Pytel
